sql_query.sql: SELECT "catalogue_productrecommendation"."id", "catalogue_productrecommendation"."primary_id", "catalogue_productrecommendation"."recommendation_id", "catalogue_productrecommendation"."ranking", T3."id", T3."structure", T3."is_public", T3."upc", T3."parent_id", T3."title", T3."slug", T3."description", T3."meta_title", T3."meta_description", T3."product_class_id", T3."rating", T3."date_created", T3."date_updated", T3."is_discountable" FROM "catalogue_productrecommendation" INNER JOIN "catalogue_product" ON ("catalogue_productrecommendation"."primary_id" = "catalogue_product"."id") INNER JOIN "catalogue_product" T3 ON ("catalogue_productrecommendation"."recommendation_id" = T3."id") WHERE "catalogue_productrecommendation"."primary_id" = 356 ORDER BY "catalogue_product"."date_created" DESC, "catalogue_productrecommendation"."ranking" DESC
